# clasp push allowlist for the Apps Script project.
#
# A `.claspignore` *replaces* clasp's built-in defaults, so we redeclare them
# here and then narrow the allowed set to exactly the files Apps Script needs.
#
# Apps Script source convention in this repo:
#   - Server code is *.gs  (Code.gs, JiraClient.gs, FieldExtractors.gs, …)
#   - UI is Index.html (generated by build.js from ../dashboard-multi-issue.html)
#   - Manifest is appsscript.json
#
# Everything else in this folder — build.js, test-parity.js, test-shape.js,
# README.md, .clasp.json, .gitignore, etc. — is local-only tooling and MUST NOT
# be pushed. (build.js starts with `#!/usr/bin/env node`, which Apps Script
# rejects with `ParseError: Unexpected token ILLEGAL`.)

# Ignore everything by default…
**/**

# …then re-include only Apps Script project files.
!appsscript.json
!*.gs
!Index.html

# Defensive: never push local Node helpers, even if the allowlist above grows.
build.js
test-parity.js
test-shape.js
test-format-mdy.js
test-incremental.js

# Standard ignores (clasp metadata, VCS, deps, docs).
.clasp.json
.clasprc.json
.claspignore
.gitignore
README.md
.git/**
node_modules/**
